Package: safecaR
Type: Package
Title: Access NHTSA API Vehicle Safety Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "W. Abram", "Astle",
      email = "wastle@tennessee.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-5162-4657")
    )
  )
Description: Provides functions for NHTSA APIs (https://www.nhtsa.gov/nhtsa-datasets-and-apis) to list vehicle years, makes, models, and variants, and to retrieve crash ratings, recalls, and complaints for specific vehicles or all model variants. Returns results as tidy tibbles for easy analysis. Requires an internet connection at runtime.
